| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1769 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f2f3b2d7-83ad-5d90-b114-ecabe91ccbd5"
